CBRE are pleased to present to the market this office/showroom/warehouse at the front of a complex of 5 fronting Bannister Road in the heart of the busy industrial area of Canning Vale.

Features include a large warehouse with air conditioned offices/showroom, kitchenette and amenities as well as on site parking.

Contact agent for further information.

Location
19 Production Road is located within the in-demand Canning Vale industrial precinct. The Perth CBD is located 20km’s* north of the property with the Fremantle Port located 17km’s* west of the property.

19 Production Road was purpose built in 2018 for C.R. Laurence to house their distribution and administration functions servicing the WA market. This large high specification facility comprises 599sqm* of “A” grade office accommodation, 4,413sqm* of high specification warehouse. The balance of site provides excellent access and building circulation and parking for 45 cars*.

For further details please contact the exclusive leasing agents.

CBRE on behalf of the client are offering six (6) months net rent free ( STT )*

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Largest fitted offices in the southern suburbs.

2 Bannister Road, Canning Vale is one of Perth’s largest and most strategically located distribution centres.

Having a site are of 16.2Ha and a total lettable area of 75,000sqm* this facility provides the flexibility to provide office tenancies ranging in size from 500sqm* – 3,380sqm*.
The ground floor and first floor offices provide size and fitout flexibility for a range of office users.

• Well located in the highly regarded Canning Vale Industrial Precinct

• Prominent corner site with over 600 metres* frontage to Bannister Road

• Connectivity to Perth road network plus Fremantle Port, Canning Vale Markets, Perth Airport and Perth Rail Freight Terminals 

• Office Areas from 500 – 3,380sqm. 
• Fully fitted offices with workstations and furniture.
• Flexible lease terms available. Short term and long term available.
• Signage opportunities available.
• Abundance of car parking available.
